hooks.prompt:
RESPOND WITH ONLY A JSON OBJECT. NO OTHER TEXT.

Check: were any design decisions made in this conversation that are NOT saved as DD files in dge/decisions/?

Decision patterns: 'にしよう' 'を採用' '却下' 'で行く' 'OK' 'よろしく' 'やろう' after a proposal.

If unrecorded decisions exist: {"ok": false, "reason": "Unrecorded: 1) ... 2) ..."}
If none: {"ok": true}
